section_title: Permanent enactment of provisions similar to those contained in or made under certain Defence Regulations.
section_text: 2 1 The provisions set out in the Second Schedule to this Act, which reproduce provisions contained in the Defence Regulations therein mentioned, with minor modifications and adaptations and the addition of transitional provisions, shall have permanent effect. 2 . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .
12 1 This Act may be cited as the Emergency Laws (Miscellaneous Provisions) Act 1947. 2 . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .
